on&#39;s Conquest\">2&#160;BC</a>–?\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Prentys_Tully\" title=\"Prentys Tully\">Prentys Tully</a> </b>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Orys_Baratheon\" title=\"Orys Baratheon\">Orys Baratheon</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>2nd <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> </b><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_7_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">7</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/9_AC\" title=\"9 AC\">9&#160;AC</a>        <br /><small>Served under: <b><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a></b></small>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\">Succeeded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Alton_Celtigar\" title=\"Alton Celtigar\">Alton Celtigar</a></div>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist mw-collapsible mw-collapsed collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Lords_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Template:Lords of Riverrun\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a hr